{"id":303032,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/冯学荣-冯学荣：《美国政府档案里的孙中山美国/","date":"2013-07-10T14:03:46Z","modified":"2013-07-10T14:03:46Z","title":"冯学荣 | 冯学荣：《美国政府档案里的孙中山美国国籍一案始末》","content":"<p><p><span>冯</span><span>学荣：</span><span>《美国政府档案里的孙</span><span>中山美国国籍一案始末》</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>          <br />\n<span>近期，我搜集到了美国政府一整套的尘封档案（当然是复印件），这套档案对于</span></span><span>孙</span><span>中山的美国国籍</span><span>问题</span><span>，有</span><span>详</span><span>尽的</span><span>记录</span><span>。档案全部是英文，我</span><span>刚刚</span><span>粗</span><span>读</span><span>完</span><span>毕</span><span>，</span><span>我想抽出半年的时间，写一本书，把孙中山这一段有趣的经历的来龙去脉以及相当多鲜为人知的细节，全部公诸于世。在写完手上的《亲历北洋》之后，我的下一本书，就写这个。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n         <br />\n<span>为了让读者抢先过个眼瘾，我先把美国档案里的主要记录大概总结如下，供大家看个新鲜：</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>          <br />\n<span>时间仓促，加上本人的翻译水平有限，不排除有少许错漏。具体事实，以我（拟）明年出的书为准。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>1<span>、</span>19<span>世纪末、</span>20<span>世纪初，当</span></span><span>时有</span><span>相当多的中国人</span><span>伪</span><span>造夏威夷出生</span><span>证</span><span>明、</span><span>骗</span><span>取</span><span>美国国籍，孙中山只是其中一个这样的人；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n2<span>、孙中山</span>1904<span>年</span>4<span>月</span>6<span>日从美国旧金山登陆，向旧金山移民局提交了骗取的《夏威夷出生证明》；</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n3<span>、移民局审查文件之后，将孙中山拘留，</span>1904<span>年</span>4<span>月</span>16<span>日，旧金山移民局作出了拒绝孙中山入境的决定；</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n4<span>、在审讯中，孙中山声称：早在</span>1896<span>年，孙中山曾经以中国人身份，登陆过旧金山；</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n5<span>、孙中山被关在旧金山移民局的木屋中，期间，孙中山收买一个报童、送信出去求救；</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n6<span>、接到孙中山的求救信件之后，美国华裔报人</span></span><span>伍</span><span>盘</span><span>照</span><span>和致公堂组织了</span><span>营</span><span>救；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n7<span>、</span>1904<span>年</span>4<span>月</span>26<span>日，</span></span><span>华</span><span>盛</span><span>顿</span><span>律</span><span>师事务所</span><span>Ralston<br />\nand Siddons</span><span>代理</span><span>孙</span><span>中山向美国移民局上</span><span>诉</span><span>；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n8<span>、</span>1904<span>年</span>4<span>月</span>28<span>日，美国商务及劳工部作出复议决定：准</span></span><span>许孙</span><span>中山入境；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n9<span>、复议决定的理由是：因</span></span><span>为</span><span>1896<span>年旧金山当局没有</span></span><span>对孙</span><span>中山当年提交的《夏威夷出生</span><span>证</span><span>明》提出异</span><span>议</span><span>，所以，</span><span>1900<span>年</span>4<span>月</span>30 <span>日生效的美国移民新法自</span></span><span>动赋</span><span>予了</span><span>孙</span><span>中山夏威夷</span><span>公民的身份</span><span>；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n10<span>、</span>1912<span>年春夏之</span></span><span>际</span><span>，</span><span>孙</span><span>中山写信</span><span>给</span><span>夏威夷当局，作</span><span>为</span><span>前任中</span><span>华</span><span>民国（</span><span>临时</span><span>）</span><span>总统的身份、表达了</span><span>来</span><span>访夏威夷的</span><span>意向；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n11<span>、</span>1912<span>年</span>6<span>月</span>27<span>日，夏威夷当局函</span></span><span>问华</span><span>盛</span><span>顿</span><span>当局：</span><span>孙</span><span>中山此</span><span>举</span><span>是否意味着其主</span><span>动</span><span>放弃了美国国籍身份？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n12<span>、</span>1912<span>年</span>7<span>月</span>16<span>日，</span></span><span>华</span><span>盛</span><span>顿</span><span>当局回复夏威夷当局：“</span><span>孙</span><span>中山当上中国</span><span>总统</span><span>，当然</span><span>证</span><span>明其乃中</span><span>国公民，但是，这不能成为我们吊销其美国身份的理由，请允许其入境</span><span>”；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n13<span>、</span>1914<span>年</span>1<span>月</span>7<span>日，（二次革命失败逃亡期间）</span></span><span>孙中山委托伦敦每日邮报记者拍电报给华盛顿当局，要求给予孙中山及其同伴予政治避难庇护；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n14<span>、</span>1914<span>年</span>1<span>月</span>20<span>日，美国驻中国公使馆拍电报给华盛顿，说：“孙中山现在持有日本护照，正在奔赴夏威夷的途中，中华民国政府要求美国政府配合、拒绝孙中山入境”；美国官方对昔日的中国总统现在持有日本护照一事，觉得很不舒服；</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n15<span>、</span>1915<span>年</span>9<span>月</span>22<span>日，孙中山通过美国朋友</span></span><span>Austin<br />\nP. Brown</span><span>致信美国</span><span>总统</span><span>伍德罗·威尔逊，要求美国政府为孙中山及其100个同伴签发特别避难护照。</span><span>1915<span>年</span>9<span>月</span>28<span>日，华盛顿回信</span></span><span>Austin<br />\nP. Brown</span><span>，附上了《中国人</span><span>入境</span><span>美国豁免签证指南》，婉</span><span>转</span><span>拒</span><span>绝</span><span>了；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n16<span>、</span>1915<span>年</span>10<span>月</span>29<span>日，</span></span><span>华</span><span>盛</span><span>顿</span><span>回复</span><span>劳</span><span>工部：“如果没有中国政府</span><span>签发</span><span>的相关文件，若我</span><span>们违规批准</span><span>100<span>个中国人入境，这将开一个很坏的先例，以后会很难办</span></span><span>”；</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n17<span>、美国政府遂拒</span></span><span>绝孙中山入境。孙中山美国国籍事件告一段落。</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/special/1265.gif\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469641,474922&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473458&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F\">青春就应该这样绽放</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469645,474926&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473464&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Funion.9173.com%2Fpub%3Fp%3D1%26u%3D1008\">游戏测试：三国时期谁是你最好的兄弟！！</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469646,474927&#